{"tid":889542,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"\u0003俄羅斯Pussy Riot露內衣快閃 黃之鋒聲援澳洲異見藝術家","createTime":"2018-11-04T15:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T00:10:20.000Z","uid":162183,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5c77a79c58be77ad406ae40c14a8b922e559d398","tid":889542,"uid":162183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T15:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMGzzDG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbMGzzDG.png&h=a60ade31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳洲異見華裔藝術家巴丟草，原定昨日舉辦、展出諷刺中國時政畫作的藝術展「共歌（Gongle）」，因主辦單位疑遭內地機關威嚇，基於安全考量最終取消。有團體傍晚舉行街頭快閃行動，聲援巴丟草，約5人參與。參與行動的黃之鋒指，行動是為了聲援巴丟草及支持言論自由。<br />\n快閃行動由一群文化人士發起，原定在巴丟草藝術展擔任開幕禮嘉賓的俄羅斯異見分子Pussy Riot亦有成員出席。參加者由中環閣麟街步行至大館，然後戴上頭套、展示標語及巴丟草畫作，及高叫支持言論自由及巴丟草的口號。<br />\n參與行動的黃之鋒指，今次快閃是為了聲援巴丟草及支持言論自由。他稱今次有內地機關威嚇巴丟草藝術展，是習近平擔心中、港、俄三地的異見人士連成一線。他又指，今次快閃行動選址大館，則因為「大館」前身是域多利監獄，象徵香港的文化及創作遭到囚禁及侵害文化藝術。他又希望社會多留意香港仍有30多名政治犯被囚禁，他們與中國及俄羅斯的政治犯一樣，需要世界聲援。"},{"pid":"6131cc0544204b204e708594616246bc5d0de34e","tid":889542,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T15:49:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f694a286bc79c477edff4c58469e792af76498f","tid":889542,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T15:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e793349f6a52af552b9505a8e1151aebdbc986","tid":889542,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T15:52:05.000Z","msg":"G 持小pussy"},{"pid":"dbc40ff803c97de8425a0cafb3ca52ee84908031","tid":889542,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T15:53:15.000Z","msg":"有團體傍晚舉行街頭快閃行動，聲援巴丟草，約5人參與。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/56fac68e17a5b69d3dd7762266d70d01/tenor.gif?itemid=10268620\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F56fac68e17a5b69d3dd7762266d70d01%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D10268620&h=15c00997&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b68959f61b1eb9639c88e289a2083440e3efa751","tid":889542,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T23:49:21.000Z","msg":"個鬼妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢啲示威應該搞多啲"},{"pid":"a67bf5760648567078ce1afec16fa7c9f71bd3dc","tid":889542,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T23:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6abd57efd6540623b11acdee86357166b0afee3e","tid":889542,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T00:10:20.000Z","msg":"Gphone溝俄妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}